 package that lets you display descriptive information about your itinerary days in each trip package. With the features and flexibility, you can showcase your trip itinerary highlights to your customers easily.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list -->\\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li><strong>Continuous Development &amp; Support<\\/strong><\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item --><\\/ul>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Like all of our addons, we provide dedicated support for any help required for using the addon. You can simply drop us a support message, feature request or any queries regarding the addon and get a prompt response.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We are also working on continuous development and adding exciting new features to the addon with each update.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Advanced Itinerary Builder is an extension for the WP Travel Engine plugin to add informative and descriptive details per day in the Itinerary section of a particular trip.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/Advanced-itinerary-builder.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 30,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 107,\n                        \"name\": \"Pricing - Growth\",