 to trip<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":127843,\\\"sizeSlug\\\":\\\"full\\\",\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"none\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image size-full\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2023\\/06\\/customize-booking-email-according-to-trip.png\\\" alt=\\\"customize booking email according to trip - Email Per Trips add-on\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-127843\\\"\\/><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You can create multiple booking emails according to the trip and customize them.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You have complete control over the content of your emails per trip, from creating interesting subject lines to engaging content that sparks their curiosity and motivates them to take action.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">2. Deliver personalized experiences with dynamic placeholders<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":127842,\\\"sizeSlug\\\":\\\"full\\\",\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"none\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image size-full\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2023\\/06\\/dynamic-placeholder.png\\\" alt=\\\"Email Per Trips Addon\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-127842\\\"\\/><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>With dynamic placeholders, you can make your emails personal by including essential details such as booking date, booking cost, trip details, and other trip details.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>It makes the emails feel customized just for the person receiving them. The add-on also helps you pull this dynamic content automatically, so you don\'t have to do it manually.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">3. Build trust and recognition with a strong brand identity<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":127841,\\\"sizeSlug\\\":\\\"full\\\",\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"none\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image size-full\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2023\\/06\\/build-trustand-recogniiton.png\\\" alt=\\\"Email Per Trips Add-on\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-127841\\\"\\/><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Create a lasting impression and strengthen your brand building with every email you send.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You can make each email personal and unique for every trip. Always sending professional emails can build trust and make people remember your business.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">4. Effortless integration for seamless email management<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":127846,\\\"sizeSlug\\\":\\\"full\\\",\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"none\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image size-full\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2023\\/06\\/Effortless-integration-for-seamless-email-management.gif\\\" alt=\\\"Email Per Trips Addon\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-127846\\\"\\/><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>The Per Trip Emails add-on works smoothly with the WP Travel Engine plugin, making it easy to set up and use.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You don\'t need to be a tech expert or do any complicated setups. Simply activate the add-on and start creating personalized emails right away.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Video Tutorials<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:html -->\\n<iframe width=\\\"790\\\" height=\\\"444\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/Th