g\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"49.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"99.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"149.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"2.1.5\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 20468,\n                \"slug\": \"user-history\",\n                \"title\": \"User History\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-09-27 07:26:07\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2023-10-13 10:50:30\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=20468\",\n                \"permalink\": \"\\/plugins\\/user-history\\/\",\n                \"content\": \"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>User History is a simple and effective addon that lets WP Travel Engine plugin users track and store browsing history of customers before bookings and enquiries are sent. With the lightweight addon, site admins can track the exact path and pages customers visited before actually making booking or enquiry.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>The add-on gives you the desired insights on how customers are visiting your website, information on the referral link and the exact path followed before actually making booking and enquiry request. When a booking or enquiry is made from your website, you can view a piece of additional information regarding the customer browsing history along with the booking\\/enquiry details.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><iframe title=\\\"YouTube video player\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/nm1P2-_s5OM\\\" width=\\\"790\\\" height=\\\"444\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"allowfullscreen\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":43478,\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"custom\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/uh-booking.png\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/uh-booking.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-43478\\\"\\/><\\/a><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>As a travel\\/tour operator or agency it is very important to get the information on how customers are visiting your website. The information is very helpful to learn about the overall site\\u2019s browsing information. Site admins can easily see and analyze the information to get better conversion rates for bookings and enquiries.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Along with the details on URLs visited, the addon also gathers and displays information on how long the customer visited each page before making the request.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Addon Features<\\/span><\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Simple and effective<\\/span><\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The addon is simple to install and use with minimal configurations required. You just need to install and activate the plugin on your site, the rest of the work will be handled by the addon automatically. Without any additional configurations, start getting the browsing history information on the site admin dashboard for every booking and enquiry requests made afterward.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Get time elapsed information<\\/span><\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Get automatically calculated time duration for each page visited by users, also the information on total timespan customer stayed on your website.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":43482,\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"custom\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/uh-booking-time.png\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/uh-booking-time.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-43482\\\"\\/><\\/a><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Referral link information<\\/span><\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Get information about your site\\u2019s traffic. With WP Travel Engine user history addon, you can easily view the information of the referral link from where customers visited your site. The details will help you in analytics and preparing marketing strategies for your travel business.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Get user history in booking emails<\\/span><\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">With the new {user_history} email tag, you can now choose to get the user history details in your booking email notification also. See all of the browsing history details from the customers right in the booking notification email on the go.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":43484,\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"custom\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/uh-email.png\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/07\\/uh-email.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-43484\\\"\\/><\\/a><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Cookie consent information<\\/span><\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine user history addon also provides additional cookie consent information which site admins can easily enable, configure and edit. As user history tracking depends on the use of cookies, you can easily inform your customers about your cookie policies.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"align\\\":\\\"center\\\",\\\"id\\\":20527} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image aligncenter\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/cookie-consent.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-20527\\\"\\/><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Gravity forms support<\\/span><\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine user history addon extends support with Gravity Forms, one of the most popular forms plugin in WordPress. With the support site admins can get all the information and benefits of user history addon even while using Gravity forms form for booking\\/enquiries right in the entry details screen.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":20547,\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"custom\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/GF-Support.jpg\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/GF-Support.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-20547\\\"\\/><\\/a><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can choose individually each of the gravity forms in your site you want to track and save user history information.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">If you are using Gravity Forms plugin on your website, Gravity forms selection settings for user history are available in <\\/span><b>Admin Dashboard &gt; WP Travel Engine &gt; Settings &gt; Extensions &gt; User History &gt; Gravity form(s) to capture user history<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\\"id\\\":20560,\\\"linkDestination\\\":\\\"custom\\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-image\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/Select-GF.jpg\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/Select-GF.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"wp-image-20560\\\"\\/><\\/a><\\/figure>\\n<!-- \\/wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Continuous Development &amp; support<\\/span><\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Like all of our addons, we provide dedicated support for any help required for using the addon. You can simply drop us a support message, feature request, or any queries regarding the addon and get a prompt response.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We are also working on continuous development and adding exciting new features to the addon with each update. <\\/span><\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\",\n        