(604, 119, 'wp_travel_engine_setting', 'a:21:{s:9:\"trip_code\";s:9:\"Bali_2024\";s:13:\"trip_duration\";s:1:\"3\";s:18:\"trip_duration_unit\";s:4:\"days\";s:20:\"trip_duration_nights\";s:1:\"2\";s:17:\"trip_cut_off_time\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"trip_cut_off_unit\";s:4:\"days\";s:16:\"trip_minimum_pax\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"trip_maximum_pax\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"overview_section_title\";s:51:\"Enchanting Bali Escape: Discover the Island of Gods\";s:11:\"tab_content\";a:1:{s:10:\"1_wpeditor\";s:419:\"Embark on an unforgettable journey to the exotic paradise of Bali, where ancient traditions blend seamlessly with breathtaking landscapes. Our \"Enchanting Bali Escape\" tour invites you to explore the Island of Gods, immersing yourself in vibrant cultures, lush greenery, and pristine beaches. From sacred temples to volcanic landscapes, each day promises a new adventure and a deeper connection with the beauty of Bali.\";}s:21:\"trip_highlights_title\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"trip_itinerary_title\";s:9:\"Itinerary\";s:9:\"itinerary\";a:2:{s:15:\"itinerary_title\";a:3:{i:1;s:14:\"Ubud Immersion\";i:2;s:20:\"Temples and Terraces\";i:3;s:25:\"Coastal Bliss in Nusa Dua\";}s:17:\"itinerary_content\";a:3:{i:1;s:412:\"Morning:\r\nArrive in Bali and transfer to the charming town of Ubud.\r\nCheck into your selected accommodation and freshen up.\r\nAfternoon:\r\nExplore the cultural heart of Ubud with a guided tour of the Monkey Forest.\r\nVisit Ubud\'s traditional markets for a taste of local craftsmanship and art.\r\nEvening:\r\nEnjoy a welcome dinner featuring authentic Balinese cuisine.\r\nAttend a traditional Balinese dance performance.\";i:2;s:363:\"Morning:\r\nBreakfast at the hotel.\r\nDepart for the iconic Tanah Lot Temple for a spiritual and scenic experience.\r\nAfternoon:\r\nHead to the sacred Besakih Temple, Bali\'s largest and holiest temple, situated on the slopes of Mount Agung.\r\nEnjoy a picturesque rice terrace trek in Tegallalang.\r\nEvening:\r\nDinner at a local restaurant with a view of the rice terraces.\";i:3;s:395:\"Morning:\r\nCheck out from your Ubud accommodation.\r\nHead to the beautiful beaches of Nusa Dua.\r\nAfternoon:\r\nRelax on Nusa Dua Beach or engage in optional water activities such as snorkeling or paddleboarding.\r\nExplore the nearby Water Blow, a natural rock formation with stunning ocean views.\r\nEvening:\r\nFarewell dinner at a beachfront restaurant.\r\nDepart for the airport for your onward journey.\";}}s:18:\"cost_tab_sec_title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"cost\";a:4:{s:14:\"includes_title\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"cost_includes\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"excludes_title\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"cost_excludes\";s:0:\"\";}s:16:\"trip_facts_title\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"trip_facts\";a:6:{s:8:\"field_id\";a:4:{i:19;s:4:\"Wifi\";i:17;s:14:\"Transportation\";i:7;s:5:\"Guide\";i:12;s:5:\"Meals\";}s:10:\"field_type\";a:4:{i:19;s:4:\"text\";i:17;s:4:\"text\";i:7;s:4:\"text\";i:12;s:4:\"text\";}i:19;a:1:{i:19;s:0:\"\";}i:17;a:1:{i:17;s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:1:{i:7;s:0:\"\";}i:12;a:1:{i:12;s:0:\"\";}}s:17:\"map_section_title\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"map\";a:2:{s:9:\"image_url\";s:3:\"128\";s:6:\"iframe\";s:0:\"\";}s:17:\"faq_section_title\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"faq\";a:2:{s:9:\"faq_title\";a:4:{i:1;s:58:\"What is the duration of the \"Enchanting Bali Escape\" tour?\";i:2;s:45:\"What is the best time to embark on this tour?\";i:3;s:51:\"Are airport transfers included in the tour package?\";i:4;s:69:\"Can dietary preferences or restrictions be accommodated during meals?\";}s:11:\"faq_content\";a:4:{i:1;s:130:\"The \"Enchanting Bali Escape\" tour spans 3 days, providing a brief yet immersive experience of Bali\'s cultural and natural wonders.\";i:2;s:119:\"The tour can be enjoyed year-round. However, travelers may prefer to check for weather preferences and seasonal events.\";i:3;s:138:\"Yes, airport transfers are included for your convenience. Our team will be there to greet you upon arrival and assist with transportation.\";i:4;s:143:\"Absolutely. Please inform us of any dietary preferences or restrictions in advance, and we will make the necessary arrangements for your meals.\";}}}'),
